== Class schedule
- Monday and Wednesday, 10:30-11:45, Moore Hall 203 ([https://hawaii.zoom.us/j/84384222329 zoom link]; password: ece)
- Office hours: by [https://calendar.app.google/mLp9CvS96utpEjDK6 appointment] or after class

== Core materials:
- Use the [https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ZX87ISNGc01UB_djdRcY4-Hv6fDj6qizkhnwX5KOAY0/edit?usp=sharing Seminar and Project schedule] to:
    -- pick your project team
    -- indicate interest in reporting on a paper
    -- suggest a paper for review
    -- find out the schedule of papers to be reviewed
- Upload the seminar materials (slides, code, links to Notion, etc) presented during the paper seminar into the corresponding subfolders of the [https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1GArIkJzJ1Phtca5Qg1_sDW1n2mOj5JwT?usp=sharing Paper Seminars Materials folder]
- Final project topic: TBD (most likely: multimodal foundational modeling for robotics from https://neurips.cc/Conferences/2026/CallForCompetitions)


